ratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "He has created things without any assistance, and He does all His Deeds by Himself without any supporters. The hearts know Him by their inner feelings and the minds do so by their thoughts. The souls know Him by their inner self-seeking His Knowledge. The intellects have sought Him by intelligence and that has obeyed Him. As He is Near, All Hearing, Present and Sublime.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "مُتَفَرِّدًا بِخَلْقِهٖ بِغَيْرِ مُعِيْنٍ وَجَاعِلًا جَمِيْعَ اَفْعَالِهٖ وَاحِدًا بِلَا ظَهِيْرٍ عَرَفَتْهُ الْقُلُوْبُ بِضَمَائِرِهَا وَالْاَفْكَارُ بِخَوَاطِرِهَا وَالنُّفُوْسُ بِسَرَاۗئِرِهَا وَطَلَبَتْهُ التَّحْصِيْلَاتُ فَفَاتَهَا وَاعْتَرَضَتْهُ الْمَعْقُوْلَاتُ (الْمَفْعُوْلَاتُ) فَاَطَاحَهَا فَهُوَ الْقَرِيْبُ السَّمِيْعُ وَالْحَاضِرُ الْمُرْتَفِعُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGree