abicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015457, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my God! Your Generosity and Blessings improve my hope, Your Protection relieves my mind. You earn no profit from my loss so I cannot accuse You of earning a lot of profit. You suffer no loss from my earning a profit so I cannot be ashamed of asking for Your loss. Then how could One who does not need the servants to pardon Him and is not in dire need of pardon be stingy. And how could He let him proceed on the path to deviation and loss while He himself has guided him. No. You are nobler than to let this happen. O my Guardian! You are much more nobler and kinder than to let this happen.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّ جُوْدَكَ وَ نِعْمَتَكَ يُصْلِحَانِ رَجَاۗئِيْ وَاِنَّ صِيَانَتَكَ وَمُخَاصَّتَكَ يَكْشِفَانِ بَالِيْ وَمَا اَنْتَ بِضُرِّيْ مُنْتَفِعٌ فَاَتَّهِمَكَ بِالتَّوَفُّرِ عَلٰى مَنْفَعَتِكَ وَلَا بِمَا يَنْفَعُنِيْ مَضْرُوْرٌ فَاَسْتَحْيِيْكَ مِنِ الْتِمَاسِ مَضَرَّتِكَ فَكَيْفَ يَبْخَلُ مَنْ لَا حَاجَةَ بِهٖ اِلٰى عَفْوِ مَعْبُودٍ عَلٰى عَبْدِهٖ مُضْطَرٍّ اِلٰى عَفْوِهٖ اَمْ كَيْفَ يَسْمَحُ وَقَدْ جَادَ لَهٗ بِهِدَايَتِهٖ اَنْ يُّخَلِّيَهُ وَيَقْحُمَ سُبُلَ ضَلَالَتِهٖ كَلَّا اِنَّكَ لَاَكْرَمُ يَا مَوْلَايَ مِنْ ذَاكَ وَاَرْاَفُ وَاَحْنٰى وَاَعْطَفُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "Arabic