iption": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my God! Please let this night end for me in a good deed that shall please You, and its good scent shall please me in the Hereafter, and shall result in Your Approval of my pardoning in the beginning and end of the month. O the Most Compassionate, Most Merciful. O Compassionate! O Merciful! Please bestow many Blessings on the Prophet Muhammad (s.a.w.a) and his Progeny (a.s) and send greetings to them many times.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اطْوِ هٰذِهِ اللَّيْلَةَ بِعَمَلٍ لِيْ صَالِحٍ تَرْضٰى مَطَاوِيَهٗ وَ يُبْهِجُنِيْ فِيْ آخِرَتِيْ بِمَنَاشِرِهٖ وَاَمْضَاهَا بِالْعَفْوِ عَنِّيْ فِيْ اَوَّلِ الشَّهْرِ وَآخِرِهٖ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ يَا رَحْمَانُ يَا رَحِيْمُ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ النَّبِيِّ وَآلِهٖ وَسَلَّمَ كَثِيْرًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": nul